# .claudeignore — keep these paths out of Claude Code's context window.
# Syntax mirrors .gitignore. Claude will not read, index, or reference
# any file matching a pattern here, even if asked directly.
# See Module 10 (CLAUDE.md, Memory & Setup) for the full explanation.

# ── Secrets and credentials ───────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
.env.local
.env.production
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
secrets/
credentials/

# ── Build output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Compiled artefacts add noise and are derivable from src/ — skip them.
dist/
build/
out/
*.js.map

# ── Dependencies ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# node_modules is large (~50 MB) and slows context loading significantly.
node_modules/
.pnp/
.pnp.js
bun.lock

# ── Test coverage artefacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────
coverage/
.nyc_output/
*.lcov

# ── Runtime data ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The CLI's live data file. Its contents change every run — including it
# in context gives Claude stale or irrelevant task state.
.task-cli-data.json

# ── OS and editor noise ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/settings.json
*.swp
*.swo

# ── Claude Code internal state ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Agent memories and session logs must not leak between agents or sessions.
# Each agent reads its own MEMORY.md directly via its tools — it should
# never see another agent's memory through the shared context window.
.claude/memory/
.claude/agent-memory/

# ── Lab solutions ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Uncomment if you add a solutions/ directory alongside the skeletons.
# labs/*/solution/
